 {\"ngram\": \"the delivery\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 837}, {\"ngram\": \"medication\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 851}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The swimmer is fine now.\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 877, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The swimmer\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 864}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The athlete started the race too quickly (she was leading in her heat after the initial 50 metres) and had breathing problems after finishing the race.\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 1031, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The athlete\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 891}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 908}, {\"ngram\": \"her heat\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 949}, {\"ngram\": \"the initial 50 metres\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 977}, {\"ngram\": \"breathing problems\", \"from\": 987, \"to\": 1005}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1030}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Potocka was later active on social media where she denied claims from her team that she had suffered an asthma attack.\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1151, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Potocka\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1040}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1073}, {\"ngram\": \"claims\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1097}, {\"ngram\": \"her team\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1111}, {\"ngram\": \"an asthma attack\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1150}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I told myself that I would go all out and leave my soul in the pool, and that actually happened,' she said in a statement on Instagram.\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1279, \"end\": 1288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.912287926582916e-16, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my soul\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1209}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1221}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1275}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Unfortunately, due to total exhaustion, I could not leave on my own, so they had to carry me on a stretcher.\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1400, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"total exhaustion\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1330}, {\"ngram\": \"a stretcher\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1399}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'No, I did not drop out or have an asthma attack\\u203c\\ufe0f I just could not breathe and move my whole body.\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1501, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an asthma\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1443}, {\"ngram\": \"attack\\u203c\\ufe0f\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1452}, {\"ngram\": \"my whole body\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1500}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'What do you think it feels like to be watched by 15,000 people?\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1567, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"15,000 people\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1566}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I wanted to do well so much, that I started too fast, but because I am a fighter and I did not want to give up.\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1679, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fighter\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1648}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It caught up with me at the end of the track, because I wanted to squeeze everything out of myself but that happens when an athlete reaches the very bottom of their strength.\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1856, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1713}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1726}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1766}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1813}, {\"ngram\": \"the very bottom\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1837}, {\"ngram\": \"their strength\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1855}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Just to achieve the best possible result and please their loved ones.\",